sure that they're more visible, that they're

00:24:20.250 --> 00:24:25.520
more prominent, that they stand out apart
from the content that surrounds it, because

00:24:25.520 --> 00:24:27.869
otherwise, it may not be obvious, it may be
difficult to locate.

00:24:27.869 --> 00:24:28.869
&gt;&gt;Meier: Cool.

